### Register Any Role (USER/REPORTER/VOLUNTEER/DONOR/ADMIN)
POST http://localhost:12000/auth/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User",
  "email": "test@mail.com",
  "role": "REPORTER",
  "password": "test123",
  "profileImageUrl": "https://example.com/avatar.png"
}

### Login (Returns JWT in cookie + payload)
POST http://localhost:12000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@mail.com",
  "password": "test123"
}

### Logout (Clears cookie)
GET http://localhost:12000/user-api/logout

### Change Password (Authenticated)
PUT http://localhost:12000/auth/password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

{
  "currentPassword": "test123",
  "newPassword": "newSecurePass!"
}